    ForegroundModule, Module<ForegroundModuleDescriptor>, SectionModule<ForegroundModuleDescriptor>, CRUDCallback<User>, GroupAccessHandler

    public class GroupAccessAdminModule
extends GroupAdminModule
implements GroupAccessHandler
    This is an extended version of the ordinary GroupAdminModule that allows administrators to be selected for each group.
    This module also registers itself in the system wide InstanceHandler using the GroupAccessHandler interface so that other modules can lookup group admins.
